value.0: The creature before you was undoubtedly a thing of darkness. With sinister eyes and the tell-tale pale skin, this was surely a vampire.
These exquisitely crafted boots are intended for those who put their faith in the powers of darkness.
These thin leather gloves are several centuries old, but due to their lasting enchantments, they still provide the wearer with greatly improved physical strength.
Wearing gloves is usually just a matter of fashion, since they do not afford any protection unless infused with magic.
This decadent cloak is intended for those who place their faith in the powers of darkness.
Cloaks are simple cloth garments used to protect the wearer from bad weather and other hazards of the open road.
This decadent ring is intended for use by those who put their faith in the powers of darkness.
This decadent amulet is intended to protect those who place their faith in the powers of darkness.
This wide, studded belt is uniquely enchanted to emulate the immense strength of the Giant race.
Belts are worn about the midsection, but do not add to the protection give by basic armor unless infused with magic.
